Package: pmxSynthData
Title: Structurally Faithful Mock Pharmacometric Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Andrew", "Stein", , "andy.stein@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generates structurally faithful mock pharmacometric event data
    by AVATAR-style profile blending for trusted environments. A separate
    calibrated structural and differentially private workflow is available
    when formal privacy is required. The package uses explicit roles, units,
    schemas, and seeds, and does not fit a pharmacokinetic, pharmacodynamic,
    or nonlinear mixed-effects model.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
